Node:	hug (Speech response to hugging force)
Input:
	struct pressure_sensor
Output:
	string hug_response: "I love you"
	string happy_color: "yellow"
Steps:
	Initialization: begin subscribing to tpc_force (10Hz)
	1. if more than one force input registered (data input from >1 topics) then:
	2. if pressure is greater than 5lbs/sq. in., then:
		(a) send request to srv_speaker (hug_response)
		(b) Publish happy_color to tpc_colors
		
		